api_list.name: Location Stories
api_list.description:
Get location user stories by using set of location ids values.  

**Location ids can be found by using /location/search endpoint**

required_parameters.name: location_ids
required_parameters.description:
Location ids should specified in the following format: **LOCATION_ID,LOCATION_ID,...**

Location ids can be found by using **/location/search** endpoint

For example: 
2082352,75929182,6811413,130521400908152,59736,1161978,221177873
